Package: dvmisc
Type: Package
Title: Miscellaneous General-Purpose Functions
Version: 1.1.1
Date: 2017-08-15
Author: Dane R. Van Domelen
Maintainer: Dane R. Van Domelen <vandomed@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of general-purpose R functions, most of which are simple functions that do something convenient, e.g. easily create histogram with fitted PDF/PMF curve, create equal-interval groups, assess linearity in logistic regression, or extract MSE from a fitted regression model.
LazyData: true
License: GPL-2
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), rbenchmark
Imports: graphics, stats, MASS
